Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.92,0:00:09.11,Default,Ashaf,0,0,0,,An Executioner!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.11,0:00:10.77,Default,Ashaf,0,0,0,,This is bad news!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.77,0:00:11.57,Default,Craig,0,0,0,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.58,0:00:13.71,Default,Ashaf,0,0,0,,That makes twice.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.87,0:00:24.58,Default,Ashaf,0,0,0,,Executioners work in pairs.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.98,0:00:27.54,Default,Ashaf,0,0,0,,You must be one of them.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.89,0:00:36.22,Default,Craig,0,0,0,,That's all the proof you \Nneeded to pull the trigger?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.30,Default,Craig,0,0,0,,You said you'd cleared me,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.10,Default,Craig,0,0,0,,but you suspected me this whole time.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.45,Default,Craig,0,0,0,,Adults don't play fair.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.17,Default,Owent,0,0,0,,What?
